{"tid":1142282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將軍澳八旬婦失足墮坑渠 露宿一宵","createTime":"2019-05-07T03:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T04:06:58.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0e06fd9400a2042e5814948e7dc732d9587698bd","tid":1142282,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:34:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zpcA4NK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzpcA4NK.png&h=e13af527&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u4W2KNL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu4W2KNL.png&h=b7f25469&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今晨7時45分，有市民行經將軍澳翠林體育館附近，發現一名老婦跌在約尺半深的坑渠內，手腳受傷動彈不得，於是報警，稍後由救護員將她送院。傷者姓鄭87歲，她事後稱昨晚行經上址時失足墮下，一直求救無援。警方列意外受傷處理。"},{"pid":"ee87a794e156f9dc2bc66f46768ab32d8ac6f639","tid":1142282,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:35:45.000Z","msg":"佢無啦啦行入草叢做乜？"},{"pid":"206f00cedd42bf8a28f34b800ea521bc67887ae6","tid":1142282,"uid":211362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee87a794e156f9dc2bc66f46768ab32d8ac6f639","tid":1142282,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:35:45.000Z","msg":"佢無啦啦行入草叢做乜？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:04:07.000Z","msg":"屙屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"574d6e0254dcb12b5739c4252c13b1a10e972016","tid":1142282,"uid":188310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:06:48.000Z","msg":"梅下梅下就入左去出唔返黎"},{"pid":"8e4dd71c9b5ebc02fe4a5ddb97d3e8b03a917ac9","tid":1142282,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:06:58.000Z","msg":"執玻璃"}]}